parameters: Yui opened the dresser.

She found a diary inside the dresser. Would you like to pick it up and
read it?
Yes
No
はい
March 4th
It's been a year since I started living here.

Coming to this town was the right decision since I couldn't trust
anyone anymore.

Since that incident, the hatred in my heart has gradually begun to
settle, little by little.
But then, I remember that person again.

If I don't throw away that hair tie, they will never disappear from my
heart forever.
Today is the day I will throw it away. I've made up my mind.
No one would notice if I did it at that place.
Only I and the eyes of the beasts know where it is.
April 8th
That man came to this town.
Did he come to mock me?
I don't know how he found out where I was.
Seeing that man reminds me of them.
I almost forgot to throw away the hair tie, how cruel.
There's a knocking at the door.
Is it them? Someone seems to have come.
This is where the diary ends abruptly.
いいえ

It seems to be a small box for storing food. A rotten smell is leaking
from the gaps in the lid.
It seems to be a small box for storing food. It's empty inside.
It smells terrible. There's no way I can sleep here.
It smells terrible. There's no way I can sleep here.
